  </a>
  <a href="#4" id="4">
   hit a mountainous section of coastal Iran at 12:30 a.m.
  </a>
  <a href="#5" id="5">
   and was the most powerful ever recorded in the area where two major plates of the earth's crust meet.
  </a>
  <a href="#6" id="6">
